com.tiyb.tev.datamodel

Class Post

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tiyb.tev.datamodel.Post
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class Post
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Encapsulates the data for any Tumblr post. This entity has the main post details, and other entities (Answer, Link, Photo, Regular, and Video) have the posts' content.
    Author:
    tiyb
